data.description: Come and see this newly renovated home in the serene Zanjero Trails community. At only 5 years old, this home still feels brand new and is in Turn-Key condition. Offering 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms all wrapped up in 2,313 sqft, the open floor plan makes this home feel large and inviting. Key features include brand new interior paint including garage, new carpet, new toilets, new fixtures, new backyard rock, professionally cleaned tile, all appliances included, owned water softener, over height garage door, RV gate, utility sink in laundry room,  and so much more.
